---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../lib/base';
---

<Layout title="About · Label Q">
  <article class="about">

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="tag">ABOUT · 소개</div>
      <h1 class="serif glow-cream">Label Q</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        한 사람 + AI가 운영하는 음악 레이블.<br/>
        세계의 전통악기 × 현대 장르의 fusion을 큐레이션해 발행한다.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="block-tag">◈ OPERATOR</div>
      <dl class="info">
        <dt>운영자</dt>
        <dd><a href="https://github.com/e9ua1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@e9ua1</a> · 아이큐 (IQ)</dd>

        <dt>설립</dt>
        <dd>2026 · Seoul · Cosmos</dd>

        <dt>현재 카탈로그</dt>
        <dd>1 track · <a href={withBase('/')}>전체 보기 →</a></dd>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="block-tag">◈ LICENSE</div>

      <p>모든 트랙은 <strong>Creative Commons BY-NC 4.0</strong>으로 발행됩니다.</p>

      <ul class="license-list">
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> 자유롭게 다운로드 · 복사 · 재생 가능</li>
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> 비상업적 용도라면 자유롭게 사용 가능</li>
        <li><span class="check">✓</span> 출처 (라벨 큐 / iq-label) 표기 필요</li>
        <li><span class="x">✗</span> 상업적 사용은 별도 문의</li>
      </ul>

      <p>라벨 큐는 <em>판매 카탈로그</em>가 아니라 <strong>공공 음악 자원</strong>입니다.</p>
      <p>카페 BGM, 개인 영상 BGM, 공부 음악, 게임 OST, 졸업영화 사운드트랙 — 모두 환영합니다. 출처만 표기하면 됩니다.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="block-tag">◈ CONTACT</div>

      <p>상업적 라이선스 (브랜드 광고 · 영리 OST 등) 또는 협업 문의:</p>

      <ul class="contact-list">
        <li>
          <span class="contact-label">GitHub Org</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/iq-universe" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/iq-universe</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="contact-label">Operator</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/e9ua1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/e9ua1</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="block-tag">◈ IQ UNIVERSE</div>

      <p>라벨 큐는 <a href="https://github.com/iq-universe" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IQ Universe</a>의 일부입니다 — 한 운영자가 묻고 답하는 같은 우주의 다른 영역들.</p>

      <ul class="universe-list">
        <li>
          <span class="universe-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛰</span>
          <a href="https://iq-agent-lab.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">iq-agent-lab</a>
          <span class="universe-desc">— iq-composer (생성 도구)가 만들어진다</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="universe-icon" aria-hidden="true">📜</span>
          <a href="https://iq-proof.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">iq-proof</a>
          <span class="universe-desc">— 큐레이션 회고와 운영 메트릭이 발행된다</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="universe-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔬</span>
          <a href="https://iq-dev-lab.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">iq-dev-lab</a>
          <span class="universe-desc">— 백엔드 시스템 deep-dive</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="universe-icon" aria-hidden="true">🧠</span>
          <a href="https://iq-ai-lab.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">iq-ai-lab</a>
          <span class="universe-desc">— AI 수학적 본질 탐구</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="block-tag">◈ READ MORE</div>
      <a href={withBase('/manifesto')} class="cta-link">MANIFESTO 읽기 →</a>
    </section>

  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 32px 80px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero {
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .hero .tag {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .block {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .block-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .block p {
    font-size: 15.5px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }

  .block p strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .block p em {
    color: var(--color-stardust-gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .info {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr;
    gap: 14px 24px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .info dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-faded);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .info dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 15.5px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .info dd a {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .info dd a:hover {
    color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
  }

  .license-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .license-list li {
    padding: 10px 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .license-list .check {
    color: var(--color-stardust-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .license-list .x {
    color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact-list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 130px 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .contact-list li:first-child {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-faded);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .contact-list a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-list a:hover {
    color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
  }

  .universe-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 24px 0 0;
  }

  .universe-list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 30px auto 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .universe-list li:first-child {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .universe-icon {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .universe-list a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .universe-list a:hover {
    color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
  }

  .universe-desc {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--color-text-faded);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    padding: 12px 24px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .cta-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
    border-color: var(--color-dancheong-red);
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(232, 72, 82, 0.15);
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .about {
      padding: 40px 20px 60px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 15.5px;
    }
    .info {
      grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
      gap: 10px 18px;
    }
    .contact-list li,
    .universe-list li {
      grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .universe-list li {
      grid-template-columns: 24px auto 1fr;
    }
    .universe-desc {
      font-size: 12.5px;
    }
  }
</style>
